## Final Resources and Tools
### Quick Reference Cards

Emergency CBT Card:
STOP - BREATHE - THINK - ACT
1. What am I thinking right now?
2. Is this thought helpful or accurate?
3. What would be more balanced?
4. What's one small action I can take?

QUICK TECHNIQUES:
â€¢ 4-7-8 breathing (4 in, 7 hold, 8 out)
â€¢ 5-4-3-2-1 grounding
â€¢ "This feeling will pass"
â€¢ Call support person: ___________

Thought Challenge Card:
QUICK THOUGHT CHALLENGES:
â€¢ What's the evidence?
â€¢ What would I tell a friend?
â€¢ Is this a thinking trap?
â€¢ What else could be true?
â€¢ Will this matter in 5 years?
â€¢ What can I control right now?

COMMON DISTORTIONS:
All-or-nothing, Mind reading,
Fortune telling, Catastrophizing

